logue quantum devices, we expect the quantum algorithm is\naccessible to current quantum technology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Feb 2022 18:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 30 Aug 2022 16:06:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-31"}
