llicities out to\n$z\\sim0.1$, so will prove useful for future JWST observations of local dwarf\nAGN in the search for IMBHs. We make our photoionization simulation suite\nfreely available.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Feb 2022 23:48:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-30"}
