estrain the ability of the detected SpyCon to extract private information. By\nhaving general detection and mitigation engines, VindiCo is agnostic to the\ninference algorithm used by SpyCon. Our results show that VindiCo reduces the\nability of SpyCon to infer user context from 90.3% to the baseline accuracy\n(accuracy based on random guesses) with negligible execution overhead.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Feb 2022 00:30:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-04"}
