 security of 100 bits for 306 bits of\nentropy for the PUF-secret. Through this, we further develop capacitive\nPUF-based security enclosures and bring them one step closer to their\ncommercial deployment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Feb 2022 10:39:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 18 Nov 2022 00:16:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-21"}
