p inspired formalism to resum perturbative secular effects,\nto compute a non-perturbative $\\langle \\phi \\rangle$ at late cosmological\ntimes. $\\langle \\phi \\rangle$ turns out to be approximately one order of\nmagnitude less compared to the position of the classical minima\n$\\phi=-3\\beta/\\lambda$ of $V(\\phi)$. Estimation on the possible screening of\nthe inflationary cosmological constant due to this $\\langle \\phi \\rangle$ is\nalso presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Feb 2022 13:58:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 16 Aug 2022 16:28:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-21"}
